### ========================================
### AUTHENTICATION (Get Token First)
### ========================================

### Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "phone": "1234567890"
}

### Login (Copy token from response)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### ========================================
### ACCOUNT ENDPOINTS
### ========================================

### Create Savings Account
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountType": "SAVINGS",
  "initialDeposit": 1000.00
}

### Create Checking Account
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountType": "CHECKING",
  "initialDeposit": 500.00
}

### Get All Accounts
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Account by ID (replace 1 with actual ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Account by Number (replace with actual account number)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/number/1234340979139630
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Account Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/accounts/1/status?status=INACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete Account (only works with zero balance)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/accounts/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================================
### ERROR CASES (Should Fail)
### ========================================

### Try to access without token (Should return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts

### Try to create 6th account (Should fail with limit exceeded)
POST {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountType": "SAVINGS",
  "initialDeposit": 0
}